{"tid":1634679,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"“差餉” 係差人嘅糧餉.....","createTime":"2019-10-07T09:25:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T05:24:07.000Z","uid":155292,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0953794b453b05b546e9641eadf61235f78d738a","tid":1634679,"uid":155292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:25:02.000Z","msg":"收到demand note，<br />\n唔想交。<br />\n<br />\n記得之前睇過有post講話遲交，佢會有附加費， 等佢出咗信追嘅時候，先交番原本amount， 唔交附加費， 佢冇得告你吹你唔脹，<br />\n<br />\n大家會唔會都咁樣做？<br />\n<br />\n仲有我打算寫信去，要求重新評估差餉金額， 原因係寫話差人服務唔值呢個價錢。<br />\n<br />\n各位業主，集思廣益，<br />\n目標係唔可以畀人釘契，<br />\n因為我將會賣樓套現走資"},{"pid":"3ebba00f84ec9908c1088d886785718d7e481c10","tid":1634679,"uid":196924,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:26:46.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;差餉&rdquo; 係差人嘅糧餉?<br />\n<br />\n改咗好撚耐啦<br />\n坐咗三十年?"},{"pid":"dca8ad19c2f1e3be3090e7a96778b3d3b1b203bd","tid":1634679,"uid":155292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3ebba00f84ec9908c1088d886785718d7e481c10","tid":1634679,"uid":196924,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:26:46.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;差餉&rdquo; 係差人嘅糧餉?<br />\n<br />\n改咗好撚耐啦<br />\n坐咗三十年?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:28:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.1823.gov.hk/big5/theme/rates/duk/origin-of-rating.shtm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.1823.gov.hk%2Fbig5%2Ftheme%2Frates%2Fduk%2Forigin-of-rating.shtm&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn%2BvO%2FPyVe1I8S2KINgfvOuE%3D&h=13978c07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.1823.gov.hk/big5/theme/rates/duk/origin-of-rating.shtm</a>"},{"pid":"e651b2b99cdfb012428d7bb8b3aab168be98a259","tid":1634679,"uid":155292,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"3ebba00f84ec9908c1088d886785718d7e481c10","tid":1634679,"uid":196924,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:26:46.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;差餉&rdquo; 係差人嘅糧餉?<br />\n<br />\n改咗好撚耐啦<br />\n坐咗三十年?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:29:20.000Z","msg":"政府官方自己都話係<br />\n你話唔係？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n餉物業估價署<br />\n香港差餉稅收歷史 <br />\n差餉 =「差人」的糧餉？<br />\n<br />\n沒錯！第一條《差餉條例》（1845 年第 2 號條例）在 1845 年生效時，的確是為了支付維持香港警隊所需的開支。當時，該稅項稱為「差役餉項」，說明了徵收這稅項的原意，現時則已改稱為「差餉」。隨著公共設施和服務日漸完善，差餉收入也用來支付公共照明系統、食水及消防等服務的開支。"},{"pid":"bdeb57fd4bacbb405f2cc78b0d91d03b3bbf8a89","tid":1634679,"uid":245537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:29:31.000Z","msg":"差餉是就房產物業徵收的稅項，是香港其中一種間接稅，所得的收入成為政府一般收入的一部分。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rvd.gov.hk/tc/public_services/rates.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rvd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fpublic_services%2Frates.html&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn%2BvO%2FPyVe1I8S2KINgfvOuE%3D&h=3def0288\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rvd.gov.hk/tc/public_services/rates.html</a>"},{"pid":"0437331745f4d73196005154e92539d51627d063","tid":1634679,"uid":40089,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:33:29.000Z","msg":"歷史由來就差人<br />\n<br />\n依家變左物業稅啦<br />\n<br />\n樓主快潛"},{"pid":"3b6c1f9f12e960c2c2db4fd6d952ba5a15c19c3b","tid":1634679,"uid":155292,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0437331745f4d73196005154e92539d51627d063","tid":1634679,"uid":40089,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:33:29.000Z","msg":"歷史由來就差人<br />\n<br />\n依家變左物業稅啦<br />\n<br />\n樓主快潛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:35:31.000Z","msg":"另外仲有物業稅（property tax)"},{"pid":"5a774274523a576f326a200e904cb30f45b60a59","tid":1634679,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:01:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cfa623caef473e491f13503a680716325cc2f84f","tid":1634679,"uid":68556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:19:23.000Z","msg":"依家係Genera